casebody.data:
Adam TOOPS, Petitioner,
v.
BOARD OF TRUSTEES, POLICE AND FIREMEN'S RETIREMENT SYSTEM, Respondent. C-550 September Term 2018
081839 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 25, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001611-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs; and it is further

ORDERED that the notice of appeal is dismissed.
